<html><head><title>Jennifer L. Key Bio</title></head><body><h3 align=center>Steptoe & Johnson LLP</h3><h2 align=center>
Jennifer L. Key</h2>

<blockquote><center><a href="http://www.steptoe.com/elecpwer.htm">Electric Utility Law</a> | <a href="http://www.steptoe.com/antitrst.htm">Antitrust</a></center></blockquote>



<P>Jennifer Key's practice has involved a variety of electric utility counseling and litigation matters in the federal, state, and regulatory arenas.  The majority of her work involves proceedings before the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission concerning the regulation of the generation and transmission of electricity.  Ms. Key has also been involved in utility restructuring matters.  In her practice, Ms. Key has focused on
