<P>From 1991 until joining Steptoe & Johnson LLP in 1994, Ms. Key was an associate at the firm of Newman & Holtzinger (later Newman, Bouknight & Edgar) where she also specialized in utility regulation
and litigation.

<P>Ms. Key is a member of the Federal Energy Bar Association and the District of Columbia bar.


