<html><head><title>Harry Lee Bio</title></head><body><h3 align=center>Steptoe & Johnson LLP</h3><h2 align=center>
Harry Lee</h2>

<blockquote><center>Litigation</center></blockquote>


<P>Harry Lee's practice involves all aspects of civil litigation.  His practice centers on the litigation of professional malpractice claims (including claims of breach of fiduciary duty, negligence and RICO violations brought against attorneys, insurance brokers and agents, accountants, and corporate officers and directors), as well as the litigation of insurance coverage disputes.  In addition to these practice areas, Mr. Lee has handled the litigation of marine construction claims, commercial contract disputes, government contract disputes, Title VII discrimination claims, conflicting claims to real property, bankruptcy disputes and claims arising under the Interstate Commerce Act and the Railway Labor Act.

