<html><head><title>Christopher T. Lutz Bio</title></head><body><h3 align=center>Steptoe & Johnson LLP</h3><h2 align=center>
Christopher T. Lutz</h2>

<blockquote><center>Litigation | <a href="http://www.steptoe.com/emplyben.htm">Employment Law</a> | <a href="http://www.steptoe.com/insuranc.htm">Insurance Law</a></center></blockquote>





<P>Chris Lutz's practice includes employment litigation and counseling, along with class action, insurance coverage, attorneys fees and commercial litigation.

<P>Mr. Lutz was author of the first draft of Chapter 30 (Class Actions) of the Manual for Complex Litigation 2d.  He has been a member of the Council of the ABA Litigation Section and served two terms as Editor in Chief of Litigation magazine.  Mr. Lutz has spoken and written extensively on insurance coverage issues,
class actions, attorney fees, employment law, and litigation techniques.  He currently serves as counsel to the firm on employment matters.

