<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Karn Decision</TITLE></HEAD>
<h2 align=center>Karn Decision</h2><hr><P>
<h3 align=center>UNITED STATES DISTRICT COURT FOR THE DISTRICT OF COLUMBIA </h3>

<pre>________________________________________
                                        )
PHILIP R. KARN, JR.                     )
                                        )
                Plaintiff,              )
                                        )       Civil No. 95-1812 (CRR)
        v.                              )
                                        )
