<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>CHARLES G. COLE BIOGRAPHY</TITLE></HEAD> <BODY><H3 ALIGN=center>STEPTOE & JOHNSON LLP</H3><H2 ALIGN=CENTER>Charles G. Cole</H2>

<blockquote><center><a href="http://www.steptoe.com/apellate.htm">Supreme Court and Appellate Practice</a> | <a href="http://www.steptoe.com/finserv.htm">Pension Litigation</a> | 
Bankruptcy</center></blockquote>

<P>Chuck Cole specializes in complex litigation under federal regulatory statutes.  The
fields covered by his practice have included ERISA, federal energy regulation, federal
railroad regulation and bankruptcy.  His practice currently includes the representation
of a creditors' trust in litigation over the collapse of an S&L;, representation of a
government agency with respect to its claims in bankruptcy and representation of a
railroad in a number of appellate and Supreme Court matters.</P>

