<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>BARRY J. DALE BIOGRAPHY</TITLE></HEAD><BODY> <H3 ALIGN=center>STEPTOE & JOHNSON LLP</H3><H2 ALIGN=CENTER>Barry J. Dale</H2>

<blockquote><center><a href="http://www.steptoe.com/corpsecu.htm">Commercial Transactions</a> | 
