<blockquote><center><a href="http://www.steptoe.com/phoenix.htm">Resident in Phoenix, Arizona Office</a></center></blockquote>

<P>Barry Dale's practice includes construction law and a wide variety of corporate and commercial transactions,
including finance and real estate.  He represents both borrowers and lenders in agribusiness loans, real estate
