<P>A version of this paper was first published by the Journal of Commerce on November 18, 1996.  Any reproduction must contain credit to the Journal of Commerce.
<P>Requests for permission to copy portions of the document should be directed to:  <a href="mailto:wbatterton@steptoe.com">wbatterton@steptoe.com</A></blockquote><hr><P><blockquote><center><A HREF="http://www.steptoe.com/pubtoc.htm">Publications</A> | <A HREF="http://www.steptoe.com/sjbios.htm">Attorney Biographies</A> | <A HREF="http://www.steptoe.com/welcome.htm">Home Page</A></BODY></HTML>
