<a href="http://www.steptoe.com/291162.htm"><I>Pesticide Regulatory Update</I> Newsletter</a><br><a href="http://www.steptoe.com/293117.htm"><i>Selected</i> Previous Newsletter Articles</a> | 
<a href="http://www.steptoe.com/envisup2.htm">Environmental Practice</a><P>
