<DOCHDR>
http://www.steptoe.com:80/crypt.htm 198.240.72.75 19970124171213 text/html 12517
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Fri, 24 Jan 1997 17:11:59 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.4.2
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Wed, 13 Nov 1996 20:40:59 GMT
