industry.  He has broad experience in Federal Energy Regulatory Commission proceedings involving oil
pipeline and natural gas regulation.  In addition to a number of representationsin major gas-related FERC
matters, he has served as lead counsel in recent and current oil pipeline rate cases for the Trans Alaska
