<html><head><title>Timothy M. Walsh Bio</title></head><body><h3 align=center>Steptoe & Johnson LLP</h3><h2 align=center>Timothy M. Walsh</h2>
<blockquote><center>Administrative Law | <a href="http://www.steptoe.com/antitrst.htm">Antitrust</a></center></blockquote>
<hr>


<P>Tim Walsh specializes in representing regulated industries in the
transportation and energy sectors, with an emphasis on economic
regulation issues.  His practice involves agency, trial court and
appellate litigation, frequently addressing constitutional
questions regarding the division of authority between federal and
state regulators.  Mr. Walsh also has acted as special regulatory
counsel in a number of major transactions, and advises regulated
enterprises on regulatory and antitrust issues in connection with
business activities.</P>

