<HTML> <HEAD><TITLE>Introducing Steptoe & Johnson LLP</TITLE></HEAD><body><H3 ALIGN=center>Introducing Steptoe & Johnson LLP</H3> <P>STEPTOE & JOHNSON LLP opened its Washington office
with three lawyers a half century ago.  Since then, we
have grown into a full-service Washington law firm with a
renowned national and international practice.</P>
<P>Our roots are in the laws of the federal government and the
policies those laws express.  Over the years, however, our
practice has broadened into a variety of areas outside the scope
of the traditional Washington practice, including corporate
transactional work, general litigation and international
privatizations.  Although we regularly represent clients before
federal courts and agencies, we have found that our practice
requires familiarity with all of the bodies that make and
interpret laws in our society, including Congress and the
executive branch.</P><P>If the legal issues are
complex or novel -- especially if they involve important
governmental policies -- we believe our experience enables us to
give superior service.</P><P>We have often represented
clients in emerging areas of federal regulation.  In some of our
most important cases, we have litigated issues that helped
infuse meaning into newly-enacted federal statutes or rules
being interpreted for the first time.</P><P>Through the Steptoe & Johnson LLP home page, you can learn more about the services we
provide. 
<P><blockquote><CENTER><a
href="http://www.steptoe.com/welcome.htm">Home Page</A></CENTER></body></HTML>

