<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Michael B. Gerdes Bio</TITLE></HEAD><BODY><H3 ALIGN=CENTER>Steptoe & Johnson LLP</H3><H2 ALIGN=CENTER>
Michael B. Gerdes</H2>

<blockquote><center><a href="http://www.steptoe.com/labor.htm">Labor Law</a> | <a href="http://www.steptoe.com/emplyben.htm">Employment Law</a></center></blockquote>
<blockquote><center>Resident in <a href="http://www.steptoe.com/phoenix.htm">Phoenix, Arizona Office</a></center></blockquote>

<P>Michael Gerdes' practice centers on employment and commercial litigation.  His
practice also includes media and constitutional law, as well as appellate work. Before joining the firm, Mr. Gerdes served as a law clerk to the Hon. William C. Canby, Jr. of the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit.
<P>Mr. Gerdes is a member of the Arizona Bar.
