<html><head><title>Robert T. Novick</title></head><body><h3 align=center>Steptoe & Johnson LLP</h3><h2 align=center>Robert T. Novick</h2>
<blockquote><center><a href="http://www.steptoe.com/intltrad.htm">International Trade and Investment</a> | <a href="http://www.steptoe.com/intltran.htm">International Law</a></center></blockquote>
<hr>


<P>Robert Novick specializes in the areas of international trade and
investment and international law.  The international trade
practice includes the litigation of antidumping, countervailing
duty, and Sections 201 and 301 cases, as well as customs,
legislative, and trade policy issues.  He has provided advice in
connection with bilateral and multilateral negotiations,
including GATT, VRAs, and Japan market access agreements, and has
advised governments in connection with GATT accession.  He has
spoken on international trade issues.  </P>

<P>The international law practice includes complex arbitration
before the Iran-U.S. Claims Tribunal involving public
international law issues, such as questions of expropriation,
breach of international contracts and sovereign immunity.
</P>
