<blockquote><center><a href="http://www.steptoe.com/govtcont.htm">Litigation</a></center></blockquote>

<P>Brian Davis is an associate in the firm's litigation group.  His
practice includes employment law, government contracts as well as other civil litigation matters.</P><P>Mr. Davis is a member of the Virginia Bar.</P><DIR><L1>Catholic University of America, Columbus School of Law J.D., magna cum laude, 1994 Associate Editor, The Catholic University of America Law Review<BR><L1>Harvard University B.A., cum laude, 1990
