<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>STEVEN J. BARBER BIOGRAPHY</TITLE></HEAD><BODY><H3 ALIGN=CENTER>STEPTOE & JOHNSON LLP</H3><H2 ALIGN=CENTER>Steven J. Barber</H2><blockquote><center>Litigation</center></blockquote>
<P>Steve Barber's practice involves a variety of litigation matters,
including:  environmental, asbestos, and noise induced hearing
loss insurance coverage; False Claims Act cases; securities
fraud; and government contracts.</P><P>Mr. Barber is a member of the California Bar, District of Columbia Bar, and the American Bar Association.</P><p></p><DIR><L1>Harvard University J.D., 1989<BR><L1>Brown University B.A., magna cum laude, 1985</DIR><p><blockquote><CENTER><a href="http://www.steptoe.com/assocs.htm">Associate Bios</a> | <a href="http://www.steptoe.com/pgatoc.htm">Practice Area Descriptions</a> | <a href="http://www.steptoe.com/welcome.htm">Home Page</a></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
