<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Steptoe & Johnson LLP Practice Area Descriptions</TITLE></HEAD><body><h4 align=center><I>Steptoe & Johnson <font size=-1>LLP</font> Practice Areas</I></h4><a name="begin"></a>
<P><center><table border><tr><td valign=top><P>
