<blockquote><center><a href="http://www.steptoe.com/emplyben.htm">Employment Law</a> | <a href="http://www.steptoe.com/labor.htm">Labor Standards</a> | <a href="http://www.steptoe.com/apellate.htm">General Litigation</a></center></blockquote>
<P>Ron Cooper specializes in the federal regulation of employment.  He has primarily
represented employers in cases under Title VII of the Civil Rights Act of 1964, the
Equal Pay Act of 1963, and the Age Discrimination Act of 1967, and the Americans
