<DOCHDR>
http://www.steptoe.com:80/282836.htm 198.240.72.75 19970124171536 text/html 40714
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Fri, 24 Jan 1997 17:15:33 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.4.2
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Wed, 13 Nov 1996 20:26:59 GMT
