<body><H3 ALIGN=CENTER>Steptoe & Johnson LLP</H3><H2 ALIGN=CENTER>Shannen Wayne Coffin</h2>

<blockquote><center>Litigation</a> | <a href="http://www.steptoe.com/apellate.htm">Appellate Litigation</a></center></blockquote>

<P>Shannen Coffin works on general litigation matters.  He has a
particular interest in appellate litigation.  Since joining
Steptoe & Johnson LLP, he has worked in such diverse areas as
attorneys' fees matters, constitutional takings jurisprudence,
and general commercial disputes.

<P>Mr. Coffin was a law clerk to the Honorable David B. Sentelle,
United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia
Circuit, for the 1994-95 term.  He is currently a member of the District of Columbia and
Pennsylvania Bars.
