<html><head><title>Stephanie L. Siegel</title></head><body><h3 align=center>Steptoe & Johnson LLP</h3><h2 align=center>Stephanie L. Siegel</h2>
<blockquote><center>Commercial Transactions | <a href="http://www.steptoe.com/corpsecu.htm">Securities</a></center></blockquote>
