<html><head><title>Alfred M. Mamlet Bio</title></head><body><h3 align=center>Steptoe & Johnson LLP</h3><h2 align=center>
Alfred M. Mamlet</h2>

<blockquote><center><a href="http://www.steptoe.com/commprac.htm">Communications</a> | <a href="http://www.steptoe.com/technolo.htm">Computer Law</a> | Litigation
