<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>KENT D. BRESSIE BIOGRAPHY</TITLE></HEAD><BODY><H3 ALIGN=CENTER>Steptoe & Johnson LLP</H3><H2 ALIGN=CENTER>Kent D. Bressie</H2>
