<P>Kent Bressie practices in the fields of international trade and telecommunications law. His work focuses on counseling and litigation at the agency and appellate levels.
<P>In the international trade area, he has worked on a variety of matters, including countervailing duty, antidumping, Section 301, export control, customs, and other GATT-related matters.
