<html><head><title>Laidler B. Mackall Bio</title></head><body><h3 align=center>Steptoe & Johnson LLP</h3><h2 align=center>
Laidler B. Mackall</h2>

<blockquote><center>General Litigation</center></blockquote>




<P>In his 35 year career at Steptoe & Johnson LLP, Laidler Mackall has built his practice on representing automobile manufacturers in products liability, warranty, retail and dealer financing matters, and safety standard regulations; representing railroads in matters involving condemnation, tort and freight claims; tort
litigation including medical and professional malpractice; aviation crash cases; defense of litigation involving claims under liability insurance policies; and real estate litigation.

