<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>MARINA T. CHARLES BIOGRAPHY</TITLE></HEAD><BODY><H3 ALIGN=CENTER>Steptoe & Johnson LLP</H3><H2 ALIGN=CENTER>Marina T. Charles</H2>

<blockquote><center><a href="http://www.steptoe.com/intltran.htm">International Business</a> | <a href="http://www.steptoe.com/corpsecu.htm">Corporate Transactions</a></center></blockquote>

<P>Since joining Steptoe & Johnson LLP, Marina Charles has worked exclusively in the East/West trade area, providing advice with respect to transactions of Western companies in the CIS.  She represents western investors in connection with the negotiation and creation of enterprises jointly owned by Western and Russian parties, and the negotiation and structuring of debt and equity financing of companies in the CIS.  She also advises clients in connection with trade transactions between Western businesses and Russian enterprises and individuals in a number of industries, and advises clients regarding the legal/regulatory framework for their activities in the CIS.
