<DOCHDR>
http://www.steptoe.com:80/Mem2pol.htm 198.240.72.75 19970124170829 text/html 8759
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Fri, 24 Jan 1997 17:08:27 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.4.2
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Tue, 19 Nov 1996 04:09:25 GMT
