<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>BETTY JO CHRISTIAN BIOGRAPHY</TITLE></HEAD> <BODY><H3 ALIGN=center>STEPTOE & JOHNSON LLP</H3><H2 ALIGN=CENTER>Betty Jo Christian</H2>

