<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>John D. Graubert Bio</TITLE></HEAD><BODY><H3 ALIGN=CENTER>Steptoe & Johnson LLP</H3><H2 ALIGN=CENTER>
John D. Graubert</H2>

<blockquote><center><a href="http://www.steptoe.com/apellate.htm">Litigation</a> | <a href="http://www.steptoe.com/environ.htm">Environmental</a></center></blockquote>


<P>John Graubert handles a wide range of federal court and agency litigation, including environmental, antitrust, transportation regulation, and labor and employment matters. In the environmental area, Mr. Graubert has handled private cost-recovery litigation as well as litigation and negotiation with
EPA and state agencies on issues arising under CERCLA, RCRA, and state environmental statutes.  He has also advised insurers on environmental coverage issues.

