<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Sue Crescenzi</TITLE></HEAD><BODY><H3 ALIGN=CENTER>Steptoe & Johnson LLP</H3><H2 ALIGN=CENTER>
Sue Crescenzi</H2>

<blockquote><center><a href="http://www.steptoe.com/envisup2.htm">Regulatory Specialist</a></center></blockquote><hr>
<P>
<P>Ms. Crescenzi specializes in environmental, health and safety regulatory matters, with an emphasis on compliance issues under a range of state and federal programs.  She works closely with clients and EPA staff on a regular basis.  She is involved with clients to support their environmental programs and to ensure compliance with regulatory deadlines and requirements.  She handles the preparation and submission of applications and required reports for clients that do not have in-house staffs.  She also acts as manager of several data development consortia under FIFRA, coordinating the data development programs and compliance with all related regulatory requirements.  Ms. Crescenzi has been involved on behalf of clients in numerous meetings and negotiations with EPA and state agencies on a wide range of  regulatory matters.<P>
