<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Sara E. Hauptfuehrer Bio</TITLE></HEAD><BODY><H3 ALIGN=CENTER>Steptoe & Johnson LLP</H3><H2 ALIGN=CENTER>
Sara E. Hauptfuehrer</H2>

<blockquote><center>Pension Litigation | <a href="http://www.steptoe.com/intellip.htm">Copyright Law</a></center></blockquote>


<P>Sara Hauptfuehrer's practice has consisted principally of trial and appellate litigation involving a wide range of issues, including administrative law, bankruptcy, Titles I and IV of ERISA, Indian law, and unfair competition.

<P>Her practice also has included counseling on issues of copyright and trade secret law.  She is coauthor of a chapter entitled Copyright Infringement published in Matthew Bender's treatise on Business Torts.
<P>Ms. Hauptfuehrer is a member of the District of Columbia Bar and the Virginia State Bar.

