<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Sergei V. Alimirzoev Bio</TITLE></HEAD><BODY><H3 ALIGN=CENTER>Steptoe & Johnson Company</H3><H2 ALIGN=CENTER>Sergei V. Alimirzoev</H2>

