<html><head><title>Cathie A. Jurgensmeyer Bio</title></head><body><h3 align=center>Steptoe & Johnson LLP</h3><h2 align=center>
Cathie A. Jurgensmeyer</h2>

<blockquote><center><a href="http://www.steptoe.com/finserv.htm">Trust and Estate Tax</a></center></blockquote>




<P>
Cathie Jurgensmeyer is an associate in the Tax Section.  <P>
