<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>DAVID S. BIDERMAN BIOGRAPHY</TITLE></HEAD><BODY><H3 ALIGN=CENTER>STEPTOE & JOHNSON LLP</H3><h2 align=center>David S. Biderman</H2><blockquote><center><a href="http://www.steptoe.com/environ.htm">
