</HEAD>
<BODY><H3><CENTER>STEPTOE & JOHNSON LLP
</CENTER></H3>

<H2><CENTER>International Trade Law Practice:  Antidumping/Countervailing Duty Law Supplement</CENTER></H2>

<P>With specific regard to antidumping and countervailing duty law, Steptoe & Johnson LLP has
represented clients in investigations before the International
Trade Commission and Department of Commerce, in administrative
reviews before the Department of Commerce and in appeals to the
Court of International Trade (CIT) and U.S.-Canada Bi-national
Panels.

