Elan Announces Revenue Increase of 70% and Net Income Increase of 39%<P>


<BR Clear=All><P>
<h3><ul><ul><a href="oct7_96.html">October 7, 1996</a></h3></ul></ul><P>
Elan Corporation and Janssen Pharmaceutica to develop once daily formulation of major Janssen Compound<P>

<BR Clear=All><P>
<h3><ul><ul><a href="sep30_96.html">September 30, 1996</a></h3></ul></ul><P>
Donald E. Panoz retires as Chairman of the Board on December 31, 1996  -  to be succeeded by Donal J. Geaney<P>
<BR Clear=All><P>
<h3><ul><ul><a href="sep26_96.html">September 26, 1996</a></h3></ul></ul><P>
