http://www.elan.ie:80/charstat.html 194.125.133.25 19970113212252 text/html 6255
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 21:22:40 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 29-Oct-96 17:27:11 GMT
