<P>
The options granted during the year ended 31 March, 1996 are exercisable
between May 1996 and October 2003 at between US$33.25 and US$40.00,
reflecting the market price at date of grant. The options exercised
during the year ended 31 March, 1996 were exercised at prices
ranging between US$4.83 and US$19.83 (the market price at date
of grant): the market prices at date of exercise ranged from US$48.13
to US$59.88. Options outstanding at 31 March, 1996 are exercisable
at various dates between May 1996 and October 2003. The year end
market price, on the New York Stock Exchange, of the Company's
American Depositary Shares (&igrave;ADSs&icirc;) was US$64.25.
During the year the market price ranged from US$33.25 to US$64.25
per ADSs.<BR>
